skdetail:

Invocation Name: time out
des:
Time Out is a tool to track time outs. It allows you to set a Time Out for up to 5 minutes. For the duration of the time out, it will remind once per minute to remain quiet and will commend on a job well done.

Many thanks to Chris Bailey (@chrisbaileywa) for the original idea and for working together in the development of this skill.

The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
